OL,3,CSandro Tonali given suspended two-
OL,4,Cmonth ban for betting breaches
OL,6,FNewcastle United midfielder Sandro
OL,7,FTonali has received a suspended two-
OL,8,Fmonth football ban after admitting
OL,9,Fbreaching FA betting rules.
OL,11,FHe has also been fined #20,000 and
OL,12,Fwarned by the FA as to his future
OL,13,Fconduct.
OL,15,FThe banning period is suspended for
OL,16,Fthe whole 2024/25 season meaning he
OL,17,Fwill still be able to return to
OL,18,Fcompetitive action when his existing
OL,19,Ften-month ban, , expires in August.
