OL,6,FHe will not serve any part of the
OL,7,Fsanction provided he does not commit
OL,8,Fany further betting breaches.
OL,10,FTonali was found to have placed 40 to
OL,11,F50 bets on games during the period
OL,12,Fbetween August and October, including
OL,13,Ffour bets placed on Newcastle to win.
OL,14,FHe played in three out of four of the
OL,15,Fgames.
