OL,3,CSandro Tonali given suspended two-
OL,4,Cmonth ban for betting breaches
OL,6,FExplaining their reasons for their
OL,7,Fdecision the independent Regulatory
OL,8,FCommission said Tonali provided an
OL,9,F"extraordinary and unprecedented"
OL,10,Flevel of assistance to the
OL,11,Finvestigation by self-reffering and
OL,12,Ffully cooperating with their
OL,13,Finquiries.JHe fully admitted to all of
OL,14,Fhis betting activity and did so in
OL,15,Fcircumstances where there was no other
OL,16,Fevidence to support misconduct
OL,17,Fproceedings.JThe midfielder will
OL,18,Fcontinue to follow a therapeutic plan
OL,19,Fand educational programme which he
OL,20,Fbegan following his initial ban.
OL,21,FNewcastle have supported him
OL,22,Fthroughout the process and he has
OL,23,Fremained in training with the first
OL,24,Fteam.
