OL,6,FTonali joined Newcastle from AC Milan
OL,7,Fin a deal believed to be worth around
OL,8,F#60million in July last year and
OL,9,Fscored on his Premier League debut
OL,10,Fagainst Aston Villa.
OL,12,FIn October, he received his ten-month
OL,13,Fsuspension after reaching a plea
OL,14,Fbargain following an investigation
OL,15,Finto illegal betting conducted by the
OL,16,FItalian Prosecutor's Officer and the
OL,17,FFIGC.
